T1  - Financial restraints in the South Korean miracle
AU  - Demetriades, Panicos O
AU  - Luintel, Kul B
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 64
IS  - 2
SP  - 459
EP  - 479
PY  - 2001
